trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs" /> that contains the event data.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs" /> que contiene los datos del evento.

trans-unit.source: Represents the method that handles the **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event of a <see cref="T:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule" />.
trans-unit.target: Representa el método que controla el evento **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** de un módulo <see cref="T:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventHandler> delegate is defined for the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Creating> event of the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule> class.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventHandler> delegado se define para la <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Creating> eventos de la <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule> clase.

trans-unit.source: You can access the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Creating> event of the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule> class by specifying a subroutine named **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** in the Global.asax file for your ASP.NET application.
trans-unit.target: Puede tener acceso a la <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Creating> eventos de la <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule> clase especificando una subrutina denominada **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** en el archivo Global.asax de la aplicación ASP.NET.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Creating> event is raised during the <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.PostAuthenticateRequest> event.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Creating> evento se produce durante la <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.PostAuthenticateRequest> eventos.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule> constructs an <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs> object using the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> and passes it to the **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule> construye una <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs> uso actual del objeto <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> y lo pasa a la **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** eventos.

trans-unit.source: You can use the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs.AnonymousID%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs> object supplied to the **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event to set the anonymous identifier to a custom value.
trans-unit.target: Puede usar el <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs.AnonymousID%2A> propiedad de la <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs> objeto proporcionado a la **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** eventos para establecer el identificador anónimo en un valor personalizado.

trans-unit.source: If you do not specify a value for the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs.AnonymousID%2A> property during the **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event, a <xref:System.Guid> is used.
trans-unit.target: Si no especifica un valor para el <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs.AnonymousID%2A> propiedad durante la **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** eventos, un <xref:System.Guid> se utiliza.

trans-unit.source: The **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event is only raised when anonymous identification is <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Enabled%2A> by setting the configuration element to `true`.
trans-unit.target: El **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** evento solo se genera cuando la identificación anónima es <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Enabled%2A> estableciendo el elemento de configuración en `true`.

trans-unit.source: The following code example uses the **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event to set the anonymous identifier to a custom value.
trans-unit.target: El siguiente ejemplo de código utiliza el **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** eventos para establecer el identificador anónimo en un valor personalizado.
